Subject: [PATCH] rcu-tasks: Avoid pr_info() with spin lock in
 cblist_init_generic()
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.1.42
Git-commit: 5fc8cbe4cf0fd34ded8045c385790c3bf04f6785

[ Upstream commit 5fc8cbe4cf0fd34ded8045c385790c3bf04f6785 ]

